item.title: About Katie
item.description: My name is Katie. I graduated from the Institute of Technology Tallaght in 2018 with an honourâ€™s degree in Pharmaceutical Science. During the final year of my degree I was lucky enough to be able to undertake a project outside of the boundaries of my modules which introduced me to Bioinformatics. The project title was Schizophrenia Analysis using Machine Learning on Gene Expression Data from the Allen Brain Atlas, I was lucky enough to have a supervisor (Eugene) who was fluent in R to help me learn about Machine Learning techniques which I used throughout my analysis .
